    function delete_pet(pet_id) {
        var xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();
        xhr.open('DELETE', "/api/pets/" + pet_id, true);

        xhr.onreadystatechange = function () {
            if (this.readyState === XMLHttpRequest.DONE && this.status === 200) {
                let res = this.response.toString();
                all_my_pets = document.getElementById("all_my_pets");
                all_my_pets.innerHTML = res;
            }
        };

        xhr.send();
    }


</script></head>

<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal fade" id="addPetsModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="addPetsModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title" id="addPetsModalLabel">Новый питомец</h5>
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
          <span aria-hidden="true">×</span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">

          <form action="/pets" method="post">
              <div class="text-center">
                  <img src="/static/images/upload2.jpg" id="pet_photo" style="cursor:pointer; width: 50%; border: 2px solid black; max-width: 300px; max-height: 300px;">
                  <input type="file" id="photo" name="photo" style="display:none" accept="image/jpg, image/jpeg, image/png" onchange="readURL(this);" required="">
              </div>

              <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="name">Имя питомца</label>
                  <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="name" placeholder="" required="">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="animal_type">Порода</label>
                  <input type="text" class="form-control" id="animal_type" name="animal_type" placeholder="" required="">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="age">Возраст, лет</label>
                  <input type="number" class="form-control" id="age" name="age" placeholder="" required="">
              </div>

          </form>


      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Отмена</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-success" onclick="add_pet();">Добавить</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>




<script>


    $("#pet_photo").click(function () {
        $("#photo").trigger('click');
    });


    function readURL(input) {
        if (input.files && input.files[0]) {
            var reader = new FileReader();

            reader.onload = function (e) {
                $('#pet_photo').attr('src', e.target.result);
            };

            reader.readAsDataURL(input.files[0]);
        }
    }

    function add_pet() {
        let name = document.getElementById("name");
        name = name.value.toString();

        let animal_type = document.getElementById("animal_type");
        animal_type = animal_type.value.toString();

        let age = document.getElementById("age");
        age = age.value.toString();

        let pet_photo = document.getElementById("pet_photo");
        pet_photo = pet_photo.getAttribute('src');  // .toString();

        pet_photo = new Blob([pet_photo], {type: "text/plain"});

        let formData = new FormData();
        formData.append("name", name);
        formData.append("animal_type", animal_type);
        formData.append("age", age);
        formData.append("pet_photo", pet_photo);

        let error = false;
        if (!name) {
            alert('Пожалуйста, укажите имя питомца');
            error = true;
        }
        if (!animal_type) {
            alert('Пожалуйста, укажите породу питомца');
            error = true;
        }
        if (!age) {
            alert('Пожалуйста, укажите возраст питомца');
            error = true;
        }
        if (!pet_photo) {
            alert('Пожалуйста, добавьте фотографию питомца');
            error = true;
        }

        if (!error) {

            var xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();
            xhr.open('POST', "/api/pets", true);

            xhr.onreadystatechange = function () {
                if (this.readyState === XMLHttpRequest.DONE && this.status === 200) {
                    $('#addPetsModal').modal('hide');

                    let res = this.response.toString();
                    all_my_pets = document.getElementById("all_my_pets");
                    all_my_pets.innerHTML = res;
                }
            };

            xhr.send(formData);
        }
    }



</script>
